- title 'Contact'
= render layout: 'layouts/partials/topper_stopper', locals: {row_top_title: 'Contact'} do
  .xw-prose
    %h2 Get in Touch
    %p
      Questions, bug reports, puzzle suggestions, or just want to say hi? I'd love to hear from you.
    %p
      The best way to reach me is by email. I read everything and try to respond within a day or two.

    %h2 Email
    %p
      = mail_to 'dylan@crossword-cafe.org', 'dylan@crossword-cafe.org'

    %h2 Source Code
    %p
      Crossword Café is open source. If you've found a bug, want to suggest a feature, or
      are curious about how things work under the hood:
    %p
      %a{href: 'https://github.com/doshea/xword', target: '_blank', rel: 'noopener'} github.com/doshea/xword
